track_notes: Parking for several cars is available at Gloucester Gap (35.265768, -82.846988).  The hike on the Art Loeb trail to the summit is rather steep at 1.9 miles and 1800 of elevation gain.  You can also take the gated FS Road 229 to Deep Gap just north of the summit on the Art Loeb Trail for the final steep climb (3.25 miles).
Track from Gloucester Gap to Pilot Mtn Summit via FS Rd 229 to Deep Gap then south on Art Loeb Trail to summit.
This is the track I took coming down.  I followed Art Loeb Trail going up.  Dean ~ K2JB

This is an epic ride from the French Broad River on a paved road for 5 km.   It then becomes Gravel at Catheys Creek Road.   Follow Catheys Creek Road all the way to the junction with Pilot Mountain Road.  Follow Pilot Mountain Road till the end of the track.  The last bit to the summit is a short hike following K2JBs track.  Beautiful views at the summit.
track_title: Pilot Mountain Activation Using a Gravel BIke
